
---
import Container from '../Container.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-20">
  <Container>

    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">Selected Work</p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">
        A few things I've helped build.
      </h2>

      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
        From enterprise supply chains to creator marketplaces, I've spent the
        last decade building systems that connect people, products and incentives
        at scale.
      </p>
    </div>
<a href="/work/olam" class="block">
  <div class="card card-hover">
    <div class="flex flex-col">

      <div class="border-b border-border bg-surface p-4">
  <picture>
    <source
      srcset="/images/olam-mobile.png"
      media="(max-width: 768px)"
    />
    <img
      src="/images/olam-desktop.png"
      alt="Olam Food Ingredients"
      class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg object-contain"
    />
  </picture>
</div>

  

      

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center p-8">

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
              Olam Food Ingredients
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary">
              Digital Transformation • Supply Chain
            </p>

            <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Worked on products digitising coffee and cocoa procurement across
              South America, Africa and South East Asia.
            </p>

            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Focused on pricing transparency, traceability, quality management
              and enabling trade in low-connectivity environments.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="rounded-full border border-border px-3 py-1 text-xs">
                Agri Supply Chain
              </span>

              <span class="rounded-full border border-border px-3 py-1 text-xs">
                Digital Transformation
              </span>

              <span class="rounded-full border border-border px-3 py-1 text-xs">
                Enterprise Scale
              </span>
            </div>

          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Katha -->
    <a href="/work/katha" class="block">
  <div class="card card-hover cursor-pointer">
    <div class="flex flex-col">

      <div class="border-b border-border bg-surface p-4">
        <img
          src="/images/katha-app.png"
          alt="Katha Ads"
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg object-contain"
        />
      </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center p-8">

            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground">
              Katha Ads
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary">
              Creator Economy • Growth Systems
            </p>

            <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Helped scale a creator platform powering micro-influencer campaigns
              across South India.
            </p>

            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
              Focused on creator acquisition, workflow automation, campaign
              fulfilment, suspicious activity monitoring and community engagement
              at scale.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">

              <span class="rounded-full border border-border px-3 py-1 text-xs">
                Ad Tech
              </span>

              <span class="rounded-full border border-border px-3 py-1 text-xs">
                Product Strategy
              </span>

              <span class="rounded-full border border-border px-3 py-1 text-xs">
                Startup Scaling
              </span>

            </div>

          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </Container>
</section>

